## Storing AI Planning Output

All AI-generated planning documents, session notes, analysis outputs, and exploration artifacts go in `history/`:

```
history/
├── 2026-02-26-auth-exploration.md     # exploratory session output
├── 2026-02-26-pm-prd-v1.md            # PM's PRD draft before it's approved
├── 2026-02-27-security-findings.md    # security engineer's raw findings
└── 2026-02-27-architect-spike.md      # architecture spike notes
```

File naming: `YYYY-MM-DD-<description>.md`

`history/` is append-only — never edit existing files, only add new ones. Add `history/` to `.gitignore` if it contains sensitive findings; commit it for team visibility otherwise.

